    "A fulltext review of these 130 articles led to the exclusion of 23 studies that did not meet the eligibility criteria.",
    "The final analysis includes 107 references, which form the foundation of our study.",
    "Review Discover Sustainability (2025) 6:23 | https://doi.org/10.1007/s43621-025-00809-6 Literature search strategyThe SLR was conducted using established academic databases such as Scopus, Web of Science, and Google Scholar.",
